item.title: 26827 - [ops2c]: * Rearrange the file so public methods appear first. Fix a couple P...
item.description:
[ops2c]:
* Rearrange the file so public methods appear first. Fix a couple POD things.
* Honestly, I'm not really sure print_c_source_top and print_c_source_bottom
need to be public methods any more. In fact, they could be merged into
print_c_source_file entirely. But separating the filehandling from the
printing is useful for testing... maybe they should be merged into a
print_c_source_contents, or somesuch.
* We ought to reduce the amount of boilerplate in t/tools/ops2cutils/. The
merge I proposed above might help slightly, but not all that much.
item.dc:creator: infinoid
